(929, 'VT000001', 138, 'after', 'This is one event jointly-organised and supported by Thai Nguyen TPO. The event served the purpose of promoting the image of Tea from Viet Nam and from Thai Nguyen in particular.\r\nDespite of late decision from Thai Nguyen and Vitas for organising this event (late September 2015, just 2 months before the event), the Program decided to go for this event as a chance to train the companies on exhibiting their products and preparing marketing materials. \r\nAt the Festival, the booth of the Program received many visitors and was assessed as one of the best booth in the Festival with nice products, nice decor. 7 companies presented their products in the booth, sent their staff in for training of receiving guests, taking documents, ... The first flyer of the group was prepared. These are essential for other international activities of the group in 2016.', NULL, 4, 2015, '2016-04-14 17:40:43'),
(930, 'VT000001', 138, 'after', 'This is one event jointly-organised and supported by Thai Nguyen TPO. The event served the purpose of promoting the image of Tea from Viet Nam and from Thai Nguyen in particular.\r\nDespite of late decision from Thai Nguyen and Vitas for organising this event (late September 2015, just 2 months before the event), the Program decided to go for this event as a chance to train the companies on exhibiting their products and preparing marketing materials. \r\nAt the Festival, the booth of the Program received many visitors and was assessed as one of the best booth in the Festival with nice products, nice decor. 7 companies presented their products in the booth, sent their staff in for training of receiving guests, taking documents, ... The first flyer of the group was prepared. These are essential for other international activities of the group in 2016.', NULL, 4, 2015, '2016-04-14 17:43:25'),
(931, 'VT000001', 138, 'empirical', 'The event must be early prepared- 3 months at least in order to attract and invite potential international buyers. Then timing should be more carefully selected. This Festival came in at the same time with another tea conference so a number of buyers could not  make the plan to come to Viet Nam.', NULL, 4, 2015, '2016-04-14 17:43:25'),
